M. A. Brunson, et al., Plaintiffs in Error, v. State ex rel. D. C. Silvers, Defendant in Error. A Writ of Error to a Judgment of the Circuit Court within and for the County of Yolusia. Stewart & Stewart, for Plaintiffs in Error; Murray Sams and Grant Bly, for Defendant in Error.

Writ of Error dismissed on motion of counsel’ for plaintiffs in error.
